<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="43">[Russia,] Sibiria Septentrionalis: Si nus Konyam ad fretum Bering, 64°50' lat. bor., 173° long. occid. (Greenw.) 28-30.7.1879 E. Almquist (S-L46!, lectotype, designated here); Fretum Behring, Kongar Bay, E. Almquist (H-NYL 3512!, isolectotype).</paragraph>
